Load Dataset

Load Data into Power BI Desktop


1. Load the Excel file and Logo from the  Click on it

2. Open Power BI Desktop

3. Click on Get Data

4. Select Excel 

5. Select File

6. Open 




First, you have to download Power BI Desktop to build this dashboard

use this link to download: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=58494
